          p.text.left.service
            strong Simple, fast and reliable
            br
            Setting up your page is super simple and takes just a couple of minutes. Yes – even you can do it!
      .row
        .col-sm-2
          i.fa.fa-heart-o.fa-5x.text(aria-hidden='true')
        .col-sm-10
          p.text.left.service
            strong Casters love it!
            br
            | We’ve developed the product based on first hand collaboration with casting directors.
      .row
        .col-sm-2
          i.fa.fa-share-alt.fa-5x.text(aria-hidden='true')
        .col-sm-10
          p.text.left.service
            strong Share with ease.
            br
            | Stop sending heavy pdf files and showreel links to casters. Create your own website and simply send them your link. Be professional!

